faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> (後備上陣一場)</span>"},{"pid":"e565613280d987bca806f387437a8f03c7fbeb50","tid":738823,"uid":52349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"pope <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209e37d90ae700c8000e0c807e64a09f0525a8db","tid":738823,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"迪基亞個時馬體都係3號門將黎，係阿辛祖同另一個都傷埋先有得踢"},{"pid":"64dd52d7dcb05f944aadb52796f1b77c9caa8637","tid":738823,"uid":32066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"細球會嘅後備龍門就慘啲<br />\n冇乜機會向上爬<br />\n但大球會嘅後備龍門根本係人生贏家<br />\n唔洗踢就有錢收<br />\n得閑出嚟踢下啲冇乜壓力嘅盃仔<br />\n又冇咩機會會受傷<br />\n萬一隊波拎咗冠軍又有機會出嚟捧埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返英超幾間大球會嘅後備龍門週薪<br />\nBravo &pound;80,000<br />\nRomero &pound;50,000<br />\nCaballero &pound;40,000<br />\nMignolet &pound;60,000<br />\nOspina &pound;40,000<br />\n就算三號門將都有成20k<br />\n你唔做我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16d01e12eb8c005cc185e90fad9e59345382b3e","tid":738823,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"一個杯賽 一個聯賽"},{"pid":"a10b471bfe033046aea0d6a41a6abd6be89d97a9","tid":738823,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"命好重要<br />\n卡斯拿斯 咁後生就可以國家隊後備入替仲要良好表現"},{"pid":"0545f4ae95ed00d481c47cdf66328ad7c68310da","tid":738823,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"仲有飛機盃踢，好似上年刺個vorm咁踢到決賽"},{"pid":"eb764b0ca7032d622113f3484a3cee52140472a0","tid":738823,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a89fd9535f8dccfc